---
import Router from "../partials/Router.astro";
import Chapter from "../components/Chapter.astro";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>
	<head>
		<meta charset='UTF-8' />
		<meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
		<title>Pixel Animation</title>

		<style is:global>
			img {
				image-rendering: pixelated;
			}
			/* vt323-regular - latin */
			@font-face {
				font-display: block; /* Check https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@font-face/font-display for other options. */
				font-family: "VT323";
				font-style: normal;
				font-weight: 400;
				src: url("/fonts/vt323-v17-latin-regular.woff2") format("woff2"),
					/* Chrome 36+, Opera 23+, Firefox 39+ */
						url("/fonts/vt323-v17-latin-regular.woff")
						format("woff"); /* Chrome 5+, Firefox 3.6+, IE 9+, Safari 5.1+ */
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body
		x-data
		class='font-code text-lg bg-primary text-secondary px-8 py-12 flex flex-col gap-32'
		><Chapter title='Chapter 1' chapter={1}>
			<p>
				In a vibrant pixelated city, MonoMax soars through the sky, his
				cape billowing behind him. He is the all-powerful superhero who
				can handle any web content challenge with his wide array of
				monolithic CMS abilities.
			</p>
			<p>
				Lately, however, whispers of the new generation of superheroes,
				the HeadlessHeroes, have reached his ears. They speak of
				increased flexibility and adaptability, leaving MonoMax feeling
				overwhelmed by the sheer weight of his powers.
			</p>
		</Chapter>
		<Chapter
			title='Chapter 2'
			chapter={2}
			question={{
				text: "Why should MonoMax drop his form handling powers?",
				answers: [
					"Dodge the infamous Spambot Squad, notorious for flooding heroes with unwanted submissions!",
					"Evade the cunning Phisherman, scheming to compromise his secure data fortress!",
					"Avoid the sinister Field Fiddler, exploiting vulnerable fields to wreak web content havoc!",
				],
			}}
		>
			<p>
				In a vibrant pixelated city, MonoMax soars through the sky, his
				cape billowing behind her. He is the all-powerful superhero who
				can handle any web content challenge with his wide array of
				monolithic CMS abilities.
			</p>
			<p>
				Lately, however, whispers of the new generation of superheroes,
				the HeadlessHeroes, have reached his ears. They speak of
				increased flexibility and adaptability, leaving MonoMax feeling
				overwhelmed by the sheer weight of his powers.
			</p>
		</Chapter>
		<Router />
	</body>
</html>
